<h1 id="organize-your-workforce-by-using-departments-jobs-and-positions" sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-personnel-departments-jobs-positions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Organize your workforce by using departments, jobs, and positions</h1>

<p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-personnel-departments-jobs-positions.md" sourcestartlinenumber="35">Departments, jobs, and positions are organizational elements that are maintained within Human resources. This article describes conceptual information about these elements.</p>
